\id 2PE - Yine NT (Piro) -Peru 2008 (DBL -2013)
\h 2 Petro
\toc1 2 Chininri Kpashiri Petro Kirukate
\toc2 2 Petro
\toc3 2P
\mt1 2 Chininri Kpashiri Petro Kirukate
\c 1
\s1 Galuklewlu
\p 
\v 1 Simo Petro kirukate. Walenwa Geso Kristo wayegreru ga wa yokanatanru.
\p Twu kiruka gixa galixachingi chinanupni, gi rixanu Woyakalute ga wa Wognetkakjeru Geso Kristo poyagkaklewle chinanu kiglepotlu wa tokanchi gixa galixanru, wixa galixanru pixkapotuko.
\p 
\v 2 Goyakalu ga wa Geso Wutsrukate gimutpotutangi ga wa ruglewanshinikankakpotutangi gi rixanu gimatlu Wale.
\s1 Goyakalu giwekle gixyawaka gapiikalunepwu
\p 
\v 3 Wa Kgiyaklewakleru rixinri Goyakalu renekwu ptowrunanuka wuwekle chinanupa ga wa wupashiregnu chinanupa wtomgajeru gimatkalewleya. Wa Walenuko royaknu yegi ga wa ruglenu yegi tomgawu.
\v 4 Wale chinanu renekwu kigleru potu ga wa tsru potu gipiratkalurkaka. Wa tyekaka chinanu Goyakalu gixpokotyawaka gapiikalunetkawu. Pojpakalu wasukyatka, wa tyechijne gajeru pojpakalu getsotanrewlu chinanu.
\p 
\v 5 Tye chinanuko psoluyako gmerewpotutanu gyognikyaplu galixlewleyma giglenchi, ga wa giglenchiyma gimatkalewlu,
\v 6 Ga wa gimatkalewluyma girukotmanrewlu, ga wa girukotmanrewluyma, kashnantakgogneru, ga wa kashnantakgogneruyma gipashiregnuchi.
\v 7 Ga wa gipashiregnuchiyma molchi galuklewlu, ga wa molchi galuklewluyma gishiniklewlu.
\v 8 Gi rixanu waneygi gixinipa tyekaka gixolewnachrikaka, waleko wane gixkakgi gi wa mmerenepgi, gi wa mkamrurenepgi wa gimatinri Wutsrukate Geso Kristo.
\v 9 Gi rixanu tyekaka waneya migjetu walenwa maygaletu pixkalutu, ga wa kmapagiruko retya. Ramtakatkalu wa muchikawluru mukochire powratikalurutkani.
\p 
\v 10 Giyagni, nomolene, gmerewpotutanu mpoyegityaplu ntomgikolu ga wa ntsomitikolu. Wa tyekaka gkamrutini, gi pagogneko gijrukanu.
\v 11 Gi rixanu wane gixa geneekotanu ponikojigloklemnupgi, wa Wutsrukate Wognetkakjeru Geso Kristo pogirewatyawaka gike rixiniko mnikawnakatu gjiglokinripa.
\s1 Klupirana rushinika Petro kiruka yonreta
\p 
\v 12 Giyagni nushinkapkakjegognenatangi tyekakapirana. Gimatmakatkalu, ga wa poyentunwalemkatkagi galikakpotunanu tokanchi gapokachriyatka, seyni nushinkapkakjegognenatangi.
\v 13 Nkagwaklu poyagkaklewluni, nomane nwinikopshini, nkomyekanshinikanutyapgi, nushinkapkakyapgi.
\v 14 Numatlu wa pshinitsonu ruknokikolupa nomane wa Wutsrukate Geso Kristo chinyawakno.
\v 15 Ga wa nmuchkowatanu wa nushpakinpatka, tyekakapirana gishinkapjetanu.
\s1 Kristo goyaknu getachineko
\p 
\v 16 Gi rixanu gi womkagitlu gimatkalewlu ginkakleshkaka wa Wutsrukate Geso Kristo giyakle wumatkakinitkagi gixa ga wa runinripapirana. Seyni Wale tsru pogirewle potu wetpotutlu wixa.
\v 17 Gi rixanu wa Goyakalu Girchiya yoptotinri kagwakpiiru ga wa royaknu, pogimewnayegitlu wane gixachri tokanchi tsrupotunanu goyaknuchyegiya: “Tyenwa Noturu nalukanru. Wale gigletanshinikanutno.”
\v 18 Ga wa wixa yijnakotlu tye tokanchi, tengogne pogimewniyachri tokanchi, wa Waleyma gawanatini wa kpashiwaka magka.
\p 
\v 19 Ga wa wanepnute poyegiru tokanchi, wa tokanchi geneklewatachinni tokanu, waneywu. Kigleru gkamrutanu wa gyanshinikanutanru wa tye, katalo pixka mapshagawaka gatajiwniyachro, gogi gimrerekamtinpotunanuko, ga wa ginshinikanuya tushpakinpotunanuko gonsagi.
\v 20 Tye gapka gimatanu. Gi satuna tokanchi geneklewatachri tokanu, yonchi gajeru, satupje yineru ginkakpokowakatyawakapni.
\v 21 Gi rixanu gi pagogne waleko rushinikanu yineru ruyakatya tokanchi geneklewatachine tokanu, seyni Giwekikaluru Kpashiri gixa ganiklenshinikanutyawakna, Goyakalu chinanu yanumatyana yine.
\c 2
\s1 Wanepna gixasha yimaklewletachine
\p 
\v 1 Wanenankoxna Goyakalu tokanu gixasha geneklewletachine yinetskala, gixatskala pixka wanepna gixasha yimaklewletachine. Pochkeruneko yoshmakanruna pnuko gixachri yimaklewlukaka gamgamenu. Wa Gitsrukaachi potu nutatanna. Walenwa Geso ragjitjerna wenruyma. Wanna gamgamenu ganikachine giyampotu wannananukopa gamgakaknawa.
\v 2 Gixolune yimanru ma pogijpatnuna. Wanna chinanu galikakpotunanu tokanchigapo gapatkalurupni.
\v 3 Ga wa gimkapnugluya gixashlu tokanuyna pnumnu yokwireyna ponikowatinna gixa wane gixlenumkaya. Muchikawayakawa wanna giklukanuwnayegjixikolu gi gamga. Ramgalepna gi wa malpokotkatni.
\s1 Giklukanuwnayegjixlewlugognepa
\p 
\v 4 Gi rixanu wa gitowrenenanu wa mukochirewatininna gi kaspukyana Goyakalu, seyni kapnakaka mapshagawaka samyokanna, gamgikowaka rumretikolupna giklukanuwnalgogne chinanupa.
\v 5 Ga wa muchinanu chiji gajenni gi wa kaspukya Goyakalu, wa ronnewkakininna psolchijne gajeneko mupashiregolunni. Seyni rumretlu Nowe, wa poyagkaklewlu kginkakletakleru, ga wa waleymana payokgipre pimrine.
\v 6 Ga wa ruklukanuwnayegjixanna Sotoma Pokchi gajenni ga wa Komora Pokchi gajenni nikatikolunna. Chichipagi rixkakanna, yaglu rixinripna wa mupashiregolune ginachinepa chinanupa.
\v 7 Ga wa koshpaklu poyagkakachri Lote. Walenwa kojwakanshinikanutkaluru wa ginanshichkaluru kamrujetachine gixjetyawaka mpogijpatnuchi chinanu.
\v 8 Gi rixanu wanna yegi rawini poyagkakachri, pagognemnunanuka saletkaluru ginshinikanu poyagkakachri retinri ga wa yijnakotinri wanna kamrutanru ginanshichkaluru.
\v 9 Giyagni Gitsrukaachi gimata koshpakletna kgipashiregolune yantaletlewatikowakaya. Rumata gimretletna mpoyagkaakane giklukanuwnalgognepotunanuko wa saletikolupna.
\s1 Gixasha yimaklewletachine yoptukyawakapni
\p 
\v 10 Ga wa wanna galikakni wa manchi pixka gixachine, wa getsotanrewlu puchotlewatachri gixjetachine, wa gitsrukaachine geyikachine.
\p Tseruwanshinikanutachinni. Wannako gishinikanru kamrujetachinni. Wanna gi pika gapatletluna pogirewlukaka.
\v 11 Ga wa Goyakalutowreruneko wanna pnute muchkonurune ga wa gimkatachine potu gi wa giklukanuwnayegjixlu gapatle ranikyana Gitsrukaachi yegi.
\v 12 Seyni wannanwa gepkoxamkojejixirune manshinikanune pixkalune. Rixa gishpakletyawaknina kashichkalunepni ga wa nikatkalunepni. Rapatluna ma mumatanutkakna. Nikatikowakna wanna koxa nikatko.
\p 
\v 13 Gektutu kamrutikna rupekotikolupa wanna gektutu kamrure. Wanna kagwaklu gigleretkaluru gogiko ponikowashatinrina. Wannanwa kapcholkaka ga wa kapatmenurunkaka. Yokwireyna meyiwatna wa tsru niklu rumnikyagina.
\v 14 Gimopatlewlu ksotanugoygalegolunni. Gi rumkata kaspuka mukochirewletna. Mpoyeginshinikanune rumlukanutna. Gimkapnuglu gasrukgajitachinni. Kamakpiiru wgenenni.
\v 15 Ruknokamtatkaluna potukgapolu, ga wa pupjetatkana. Walaami Wosoro wgenegapo romkagitna. Walenwa mpoyagkaknuchi wenutikolu gishinikachri.
\v 16 Chigetjetka waleko mukochire chinanu. Mtokanuto mporo, yineru tokanu yanumatyachro, gijretlu tokanchi geneklewatachri seprolokinri.
\s1 Pojpakalu wayegrene
\p 
\v 17 Wannanwa gonu gishpakgatyawakmaka magatu pixkalune. Ga wa kyachgapereru gichkonnipgyalu ganikanru pixkalune. Wanna chinanu gimretkalurni mapshagalsajnu.
\v 18 Gi rixanu magijeru tokanushatna tsrupotunanu tokanchi wa manchi getsotanrewleya rumlukikolunapna gajeryako gasukachine wa pupjeru gixjetachinyegiya.
\v 19 Rushpakinripna gipiratikalunni, seyni wa gipiratachineko pojpakalu wayegrene rixna. Gi rixanu klunerukokta gaalixlu yineru, wale chinanu wayegretika yineru.
\v 20 Gi rixanu wa Gitsrukaachi Gognetkaklewatachri Geso Kristo rumatkalchinanna wanna, rasukinitkaluna tyechijne gajeru puchotlewatachri ga wa wanepnute yoshmaakana, ralipretinrina gektutu rixa yinuwakinrina pnute.
\v 21 Gi rixanu kiglemkalu wanna chinanu ma mumatkanumkaluna poyagkaklewlugapo, wanepnute rumatinmakluna ga wa satokyegitinmakluna kpashiri yokanrukaka, wa wanna geneekaluru.
\v 22 Wane rixatkana galikakpotunanu yapkaklu:
\q1 \qt Kewe satokyegitlu waleko raplire. \qt*
\q1 \qt Ga wa kochi gerkakalurutka \qt*
\q2 \qt satoka posujpalu yegi ruprurugatinripa. \qt*
\c 3
\s1 Ralipregognekakapa runanna kgixpiranataklerune
\p 
\v 1 Nushinikanune, twunwa gepi chininro kiruka nyonyegityagi. Twu kiruukakaya nkomyekanshinikanutgi ginshinikanuya powralu, nushinkapkakyapgi.
\v 2 Gishinikyaplu tokanchi muchinanu chinkaluru kpashirine tokanchi geneklewatachinniya, ga wa Gitsrukaachi Gognetkaklewatachri yokanre gixa yegi yokanatkaluneya.
\p 
\v 3 Muchinanu gapka gimatanru tye, wa ralipregognekakapa runanna kgixpiranataklerune. Ruxpiranatlewatanna. Rixa getsotanretyawakna rixjetanna.
\v 4 Wane chinanna, “¿Ginaklu gipiratkaluru Geso gininripapirana? Gi rixanu wa gitsrukaachinni gapnanutiniyakawa rixyawakakni ptowrunanuka reyinuwakleyakawa giyakotkalurkaka.”
\p 
\v 5 Gi rixanu wannako ginshinikanuyna gi rumatluna wa muchikawako wanetkalu tengogne ga wa chiji, gonu gimlikyachri ga wa gonu gwachri. Goyakalu tokanu chinanu rixkakikowakni.
\v 6 Giyagni tye gonu muchikawa gwachrini chiji gonnewatachrini nikawna.
\v 7 Ga wa xawakni gwachri tengogne ga wa chiji Wale tokanuya gimretkalurni xirnachri chinanupa, tsru giklukanuwnalgognepotunanuko, yine mupashiregolune gamginrigognepatka.
\s1 Gitsrukaachigognepa ginanu
\p 
\v 8 Giyagni gixa, nushinikanune, gi wa mumatkanepgi tyepirana, wa Gitsrukaachi getanu satu waragka walapu pixka rixa pagognepje, ga wa pagognepje pixka rixa satu waragka walapu.
\v 9 Wa Gitsrukaachi gi kaptotyalu rupiratanruya wa pimrine kagwakyaluna kaptotinri. Seyni mapognanutu rixyegitwu. Gi raluklu satuna gamginripa, seyni pejnuruneko yoptotanru genshinikanrewlu.
\p 
\v 10 Ga wa Gitsrukaachigognepa kachowguru pixka rixa gapokletanu. Walegogne tsru sejrewakchiya nikawnanu tengogne. Ga wa tyegogne gajerkaka yochpiikalurupni nikawnanu. Ga wa chiji koxa ga wa chiji gajerkaka kamrurchi nikawnanu.
\s1 Gerotu tengogne ga wa gerotu chiji
\p 
\v 11 Gi rixanu pejnuruko tyekaka nikawnachripni, ¿gi pixkalune gimkata gixleta? Kpashirinepgi ga wa kagwakpiraklerunepgi.
\v 12 Kagwakachinepgi ga wa jmererunepgi Goyakalgogne gapokinipa. Gigogne gapokinri chinanu tengogne galgachripa nikawnanu, ga wa tyegogne gajerkaka yochpiikalurupa rupragkanu.
\v 13 Seyni wkagwaklu gerotu tengogne ga wa gerotu chiji wa rixa gipiiretyawaka, wa poyagkaklewlu gwiyawakapa.
\s1 Wuykotka galpokotachinepwu wixinripa
\p 
\v 14 Giyagni, nushinikanune, tyekaka gkagwakanatini, gyagota mapchone gixleta Goyakalu getanu, ga wa muklukanuwnakanepgi Waleya giglewanshinikanrewleymapa.
\v 15 Ga wa gyanshinikanutanru wa Wutsrukate ma mapognannu gognewatikaluru rixinri, china yonyegletyawakgi wushinikanru wumole Pawlo, rixa genekashletikowaka rumatkalewle.
\v 16 Wane rixyawaka, wa pejnuruko kirukatkakaya, tyepirankakaya runkaklewatya. Wa twukakaya waneru kgimalu tokanchikaka, wa myimaakone ga wa mpoyeginshinikanune katpa rixkakluna, pimri yonatkaluru koxa pixka, wannako ramginripna chinanu.
\p 
\v 17 Giyagni gixa, nushinikanune, gimatagnaputinri, gimretinwa. Wa ginanshichkaluru kamrujetachine pupjere gma kosetikotupa, gixanuko poyentunwaleya gma mujrukinitipa.
\v 18 Seyni ntseruwnanu gimutlewluya ga wa rumatikoluya Wutsrukate Wognetkakjeru Geso Kristo. Walenni wa goyaknuchi xawakni ga wa psolgogneshpotunanuko mnikawnakatupa.
